lead_paragraph: Rival managers Alex Neil and Rafa Benitez are trying to play down the importance of what many supporters have called a "must- win" Premier League relegation game between Norwich City and Newcastle United on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Norwich, Newcastle Managers Play Down Crunch Game
